            "title": "盤中速報 - 旭隼(6409)大跌7.07%，報855元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>旭隼(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6409:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6409\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6409-TW</a>)30日13:20股價下跌65元，報855.0元，跌幅7.07%，成交1,246張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>旭隼(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6409:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6409\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6409-TW</a>)所屬產業為其他電子業，主要業務為UPS(Uninterruptible power system)。INVERTER/PV INVERTER / AVR / Electronic Components。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價下跌1.81%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲2.49%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+112 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+258 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：-117 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-29 張</li> <li>融資增減：+66 張</li> <li>融券增減：-2 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
